column3: Post Message
column8: Lifetime: The number of people who saw your Page post. (Unique Users)
column9: Lifetime: The number of people who saw your Page post in news feed or ticker, or on your Page's timeline. (Unique Users)
column10: Lifetime: The number of people who saw your Page post in an ad or sponsored story. (Unique Users)
column11: Lifetime: The number of impressions of your Page post. (Total Count)
column12: Lifetime: The number of impressions of your post in News Feed or ticker or on your Page's Wall. (Total Count)
column13: Lifetime: The number of impressions of your Page post in an Ad or Sponsored Story. (Total Count)
column14: Lifetime: The number of people who clicked anywhere in your posts. (Unique Users)
column15: Lifetime: The number of unique people who created a story about your Page post by interacting with it. (Unique Users) - comment
column16: Lifetime: The number of unique people who created a story about your Page post by interacting with it. (Unique Users) - like
column17: Lifetime: The number of unique people who created a story about your Page post by interacting with it. (Unique Users) - share
column18: Lifetime: The number of stories created about your Page post, by action type. (Total Count) - comment
column19: Lifetime: The number of stories created about your Page post, by action type. (Total Count) - like
column20: Lifetime: The number of stories created about your Page post, by action type. (Total Count) - share
column21: Lifetime: The number of people who clicked anywhere in your post. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Unique Users)
column22: Lifetime: The number of clicks anywhere in your post. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Total Count)
column23: Lifetime: The number of people who clicked anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Unique Users) - link clicks
column24: Lifetime: The number of people who clicked anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Unique Users) - other clicks
column25: Lifetime: The number of people who clicked anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Unique Users) - photo view
column26: Lifetime: The number of clicks anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Total Count) - link clicks
column27: Lifetime: The number of clicks anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Total Count) - other clicks
column28: Lifetime: The number of clicks anywhere in your post, by type. Clicks generating stories are included in "Other Clicks." (Total Count) - photo view
column29: Lifetime: The number of people who have given negative feedback to your post. (Unique Users)
column30: Lifetime: The number of times people have given negative feedback to your post. (Total Count)
column31: Lifetime: The number of people who have given negative feedback to your post, by type. (Unique Users) - xbutton_clicks
column32: Lifetime: The number of times people have given negative feedback to your post, by type. (Total Count) - xbutton_clicks
column33: Lifetime: The number of impressions of your Page post to people who have liked your Page. (Total Count)
column34: Lifetime: The number of people who saw your Page post because they've liked your Page (Unique Users)
column35: Lifetime: The number of paid impressions of your Page post to people who have liked your Page. (Total Count)
column36: Lifetime: The number of people who like your Page and who saw your Page post in an ad or sponsored story. (Unique Users)
column37: Lifetime: The number of people who have liked your Page and clicked anywhere in your posts. (Unique Users)
